options.heywiki.raycast_reach.descriptio:
Maximum distance you can aim at to trigger the Hey Wiki feature.
Note that higher values may cause performance issues.
If interaction range attribute is higher, it will be used instead.
options.heywiki.raycast_reach.name: Reach
options.heywiki.requires_confirmation.de:
Open confirmation screen before opening the wiki article.
This is useful to avoid accidentally triggering the feature or to see a preview of the wiki page.
options.heywiki.requires_confirmation_co:
When using a command, open confirmation screen before opening the wiki article.
This is useful to if you still want the preview screen when using a command.
